data.description: This home is situated nicely on 23.87 acres with beautiful views. It is spacious and offers hardwood flooring on the first and second floors, a Mother-in-law Suite, three full baths and 1 half bath, large kitchen, formal dining, an office, 3 bedrooms, a spacious attic with a thermostatic controlled fan, separate laundry room and a two-car garage. Exterior features include a swimming pool with a stamped concrete surround, a built in BBQ/Bar Area and beautiful landscaping! That's not all...Bring the Horses! There is a 36x36 Barn, Fenced Pastures with more land to expand, and an Equipment Shed. Located conveniently to I64 and halfway between Charlottesville and Richmond!
